Rb3 regulated caspase 3, caspase 8, and caspase 9 in GP-293 cells. (a) Elisa assay for the activities of caspase 3, caspase 8, and caspase 9. (b) Western blotting for the cleavage levels of caspase 3, caspase 8, and caspase 9. (c) Quantitative analysis of densitometry for the cleavage levels of caspase 3, caspase 8, and caspase 9.
